#: upstream/_posts/2020-10-05-contributing-for-the-first-time.adoc:112
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "*core*: this is the core runtime and deployment modules of Quarkus. Ask for help if you want to contribute in it.\n"
msgstr "*core*: es el núcleo de los módulos de ejecución y despliegue de Quarkus. Pide ayuda si quieres contribuir en él."

#. type: Plain text
#: upstream/_posts/2020-10-05-contributing-for-the-first-time.adoc:113
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "*devtools*: where the Maven and Gradle plugins lies.\n"
